{"tid":1818074,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"睇完燒山既 給香港人的一封家書 有小小想法","createTime":"2020-01-09T15:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T19:39:00.000Z","uid":345002,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0f5f3b23442cb0873d7cdf611ef93141d1ad16","tid":1818074,"uid":345002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">頭先睇完燒山 給香港人的一封家書 段片, 講到今次運動好驚會去返雨傘咁, 團火自然熄滅, 然後就秋後算帳. 唔想秋後算帳只要唔好比團火熄, 就同港共,中共鬥長命, 我地就會羸</span><br />\n<br />\n以下有小小建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.每個月一次大型遊行</span></span><br />\n每個月遊行一次, 燃起返團火, 聚集返香港人<br />\n(可能有人話, 依家遊行有咩用? 送頭? )<br />\n遊行目的只要係聚集返香港人, 運動未完, 唔係期望政府咩有咩回應. (最重要都係不被捕)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.每月不可少「和你SUCK, 和你唱, 連儂日, 幫襯黃店」等等</span></span><br />\n呢D活動主要係打擊經濟, 要港共,中共驚. 一齊攬炒 (最重要都係不被捕)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要唔比團火熄,每個月都重覆咁做, 我地實會贏<br />\n其實方法好簡單, 係睇大家有無恆心去做. </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> <span style=\"color: pink;\">鬥長命就會贏</span></span>"},{"pid":"892cee2de021ea6e0d3fc5f32edd726a1f583536","tid":1818074,"uid":135277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c606beb464cc35967f8c576a94dcb553774b863e","tid":1818074,"uid":135277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4b1c1bb485ba8f8c7742362c4117602d2c0ebf","tid":1818074,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:53:31.000Z","msg":"佢好似唔係咁講喎<br />\n乜佢唔係話要有人整合下件事咩<br />\n自己做唔到都要HUR泛民"},{"pid":"b429966682e633c056799e372e4aacd5e9edcc0a","tid":1818074,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-